# WF-22 SUMMARY (22 × 45-day windows, 2025-05-21 to 2026-04-01):
#   AvgPF:     1.421
#   PF>1.00:   14/22 (64%)
#   PF>1.15:   14/22 (64%)
#   AvgTrades: ~13/window
#
# STRONG windows: May-21, Jun-05, Jun-20, Jul-05, Jul-20,
#                 Sep-03, Sep-18, Dec-17, Jan-01, Jan-31,
#                 Feb-15, Mar-02, Mar-17, Apr-01
# WEAK windows:   Aug-04, Aug-19, Oct-03, Oct-18, Nov-02,
#                 Nov-17, Dec-02, Jan-16
#
# NOTE: Nov 2025 was BTC's strong bull run ATH $108k push —
# bounce strategy fires fewer winning trades in one-directional
# uptrends (price doesn't pull back enough to support levels).
# Consider disabling during extreme bull/bear momentum runs.
